{
	"nodes":[
		{
			"id":"47f1d61aa2f76524",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## llm的system promts或者tools入参中，描述调用工具A的时机以及格式\n\n以天气查询为例。系统提示词这么写：\n```\n如果用户有查询天气相关的请求，则需要使用<weather-tools>工具，请你先返回查询语句，格式如下。\n```",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-220,
			"y":-220,
			"width":422,
			"height":331
		},
		{
			"id":"89437081cea64c19",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## LLM 意图识别成功后，将返回tools调用参数\n比如也可以直接指定llm返回json格式：\n```json\n{\n\t\"location\": \"北京\",\n\t\"time\": 98898312\n}\n```",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":360,
			"y":-220,
			"width":340,
			"height":331
		},
		{
			"id":"a9ae3944c3971c1b",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 后端解析llm返回的工具调用参数，调用api进行查询",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-220,
			"y":180,
			"width":422,
			"height":139
		},
		{
			"id":"c1a2b3c4d5e6f701",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 用户输入 / 问题\n例如：\n- 明天北京天气？\n- 帮我查下明天是否下雨",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-620,
			"y":-220,
			"width":300,
			"height":160
		},
		{
			"id":"mcpflow000000001",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## MCP 工具调用（高层流程）\n- 客户端与 MCP 服务器建立会话（Stdio / WebSocket）\n- 列出工具 listTools，选择合适工具\n- 以 callTool 发送结构化参数\n- 工具执行并可能以流式/分块返回结果\n- 客户端整合并返回给 LLM/用户",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":880,
			"y":-240,
			"width":420,
			"height":240
		},
		{
			"id":"mcptools000000001",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 关键要点（MCP）\n- 请求/响应包裹 JSON-RPC 风格，含 id、method、params\n- 能力：listTools、callTool、资源访问等\n- 安全：工具白名单、沙箱、超时、参数校验\n- 可观测：记录调用链路、错误、耗时",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":880,
			"y":40,
			"width":420,
			"height":220
		},
		{
			"id":"gomcp0000000001",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Go 片段：调用 MCP 工具（WebSocket 示例）\n```go\nimport (\n    \"encoding/json\"\n    \"log\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/gorilla/websocket\"\n)\n\ntype Request struct {\n    JSONRPC string      `json:\"jsonrpc\"`\n    ID      int         `json:\"id\"`\n    Method  string      `json:\"method\"`\n    Params  interface{} `json:\"params\"`\n}\n\nfunc callMCP() error {\n    conn, _, err := websocket.DefaultDialer.Dial(\"ws://localhost:8080/mcp\", nil)\n    if err != nil { return err }\n    defer conn.Close()\n\n    req := Request{\n        JSONRPC: \"2.0\",\n        ID:      1,\n        Method:  \"tools/call\",\n        Params: map[string]any{\n            \"name\": \"search\",\n            \"arguments\": map[string]any{\"q\": \"obsidian canvas 规范\"},\n        },\n    }\n\n    if err := conn.WriteJSON(req); err != nil { return err }\n\n    conn.SetReadDeadline(time.Now().Add(10 * time.Second))\n    var resp map[string]any\n    if err := conn.ReadJSON(&resp); err != nil { return err }\n\n    log.Println(\"MCP result:\", resp)\n    return nil\n}\n```",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":1320,
			"y":-100,
			"width":520,
			"height":460
		},
		{
			"id":"errorsafety0000001",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 错误与重试（要点）\n- 参数 JSON Schema 校验失败 → 要求模型重试\n- 工具超时/异常 → 降级回答或兜底提示\n- 记录调用日志（prompt、args、latency）",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":576,
			"y":229,
			"width":360,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"goopenai00000001",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Go 片段：OpenAI Function Calling（工具定义与解析）\n```go\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"encoding/json\"\n    \"os\"\n\n    openai \"github.com/sashabaranov/go-openai\"\n)\n\ntype WeatherArgs struct {\n    Location string `json:\"location\"`\n    Time     int64  `json:\"time,omitempty\"`\n}\n\nfunc callWithTool() {\n    client := openai.NewClient(os.Getenv(\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"))\n    schema := map[string]any{\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": map[string]any{\n            \"location\": map[string]any{\"type\":\"string\"},\n            \"time\":     map[string]any{\"type\":\"integer\"},\n        },\n        \"required\": []string{\"location\"},\n    }\n\n    req := openai.ChatCompletionRequest{\n        Model: \"gpt-4o-mini\",\n        Messages: []openai.ChatCompletionMessage{\n            {Role: \"system\", Content: \"你是天气助手\"},\n            {Role: \"user\", Content: \"明天北京天气怎么样？\"},\n        },\n        Tools: []openai.Tool{\n            {Type: openai.ToolTypeFunction, Function: &openai.FunctionDefinition{\n                Name: \"get_weather\",\n                Description: \"查询天气\",\n                Parameters: schema,\n            }},\n        },\n    }\n\n    resp, _ := client.CreateChatCompletion(context.Background(), req)\n    for _, tc := range resp.Choices[0].Message.ToolCalls {\n        if tc.Function.Name == \"get_weather\" {\n            var args WeatherArgs\n            _ = json.Unmarshal([]byte(tc.Function.Arguments), &args)\n            // 调用你的后端/外部API...\n            // 然后将工具结果作为新消息反馈给模型\n        }\n    }\n}\n```",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-260,
			"y":409,
			"width":620,
			"height":500
		},
		{
			"id":"toolresultround01",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 将工具结果反馈给 LLM\n\n- 以 function_call 的 function result / tool result 形式返回给模型\n- LLM 再次推理并融合工具结果",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":487,
			"y":479,
			"width":320,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"finalanswer000001",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 最终回答\n- 直接回答用户问题\n- 保留必要出处/单位/时间",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":880,
			"y":499,
			"width":260,
			"height":160
		}
	],
